title: Stak'd Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. They offer made-in-house black bean burgers which can be substituted for anything on the menu. They also offer five bun options (including gluten-free) and Vegan cheese and mayonnaise. They also have Veg and Vegan-friendly sides and salads.  Friendly, helpful staff.
